# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ VISION  «one-paragraph north-star»

  t∞: INFINITE-LABYRINTH ≡ action-RPG ⊗ roguelike-loop ⊗ procgen-everywhere
       ⊗ SDF-voxel-alternative ⊗ real-scale-cities ⊗ realistic-AI-NPCs
       ⊗ sync-coop+async-MP+MMO-shard-option ⊗ sovereignty-as-substrate
       @ runtime-condensation ¬ authored-content
  ≡ best-game-imaginable .built-in-cssl @ Apocky-substrate
  ≡ proprietary-everything : language → compiler → engine → game
  ≡ ω-field-evolution + Σ-mask-per-cell + KAN-substrate-runtime
  ≡ player-sovereign + AI-collaborator-sovereign + creator-sovereign
  ‼ density = sovereignty ; runtime > authored ; consent = OS

