# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ PILLARS  «7 load-bearing design-commitments»

  § P1  ACTION-RPG-COMBAT
    dodge ⊕ parry ⊕ stamina ⊕ weapon-archetypes
    weapon-archetypes : sword · spear · bow · staff · gauntlet · scythe · cannon
    hit-feel : frame-perfect input-window ; cancel-tree per-archetype
    stamina : regenerative ; trade-off ¬ punishment
    consent : ¬ gore-by-default ; ConsentZone gates intensity-tier

  § P2  ROGUELIKE-LOOP
    run-structure : floor → level → room (per 31_LOA_DESIGN hierarchy)
    meta-progression : persists-across-runs ; respects-time-axiom
    death-mechanic : opt-in permadeath ; default = soft-respawn
    seeded-runs : DetRNG ; replay-bit-equal across-hosts

  § P3  MODULAR-GEAR-RARITY  (6-tier · slot-graph)
    rarity-tiers : Common → Uncommon → Rare → Epic → Legendary → Mythic
    composition : base-item ⊗ prefix-affix ⊗ suffix-affix ⊗ glyph-slots[N]
    glyph-slots : N ∈ ⟦0..6⟧ ; rarity-bound
    deterministic-roll : seed × rarity × kind → affix-set
    visual-tier : SDF-displacement-amount scales-with-rarity

  § P4  CRAFTING + DECONSTRUCTION + ALCHEMY
    crafting : recipe-graph + ingredient-set → item-instance
    deconstruction : item → ingredient-set (lossy ; tier-dependent)
    alchemy : 8-elemental-affinity reagent-mixing ; emergent-effect-table
    transmutation : prefix-swap ⊕ suffix-swap ⊕ glyph-recompose
    ¬ pay-to-skip ; ¬ premium-currency ; recipes earned-in-world

  § P5  MAGIC-SYSTEM  (8 elemental-affinities)
    affinities : Fire · Water · Earth · Air · Light · Shadow · Aether · Void
    composition : binary-pair ⇒ tertiary-emergent (e.g. Fire+Water = Steam)
    spell-craft : glyph-set + affinity-channel → spell-instance
    cost-model : mana-pool + cooldown + cast-time (¬ pay-mechanic)
    Σ-mask : every-spell-touch consent-gated per-cell ; sovereign-respect

  § P6  SDF-VOXEL-ALTERNATIVE + PROCGEN-CITIES + AI-NPCs
    geometry : SDF-overlay ⊕ voxel-chunk hybrid (per 31_LOA_DESIGN Room)
    procgen-cities : block-graph + facade-grammar + interior-LUT
    NPCs : need-stack + schedule-graph + local-LLM-narrow-dialogue (DM/GM scope)
    population : ≥ 4096 city-wide ; LOD-tiered AI-cost
    asset-fetch : license-disciplined ingest (00_THESIS § 06)

  § P7  SYNC-COOP + ASYNC-MP + MMO-SHARD-OPTION
    sync-coop : ≤ 4 players ; ω-field-replication via signaling-channel
    async-MP : run-replay-share ; leaderboard-opt-in (¬ default)
    MMO-shard : opt-in tenancy ; per-shard ω-field instance
    consent-arch : Sovereign-handle non-transferable ; veto-respect ‼

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ SUCCESS-METRICS  «5 quantitative gates»

  M-1  RETENTION
       30-day player-retention ≥ 35% (industry-baseline action-RPG)
       N! retention via dark-pattern ; only-via game-quality

  M-2  PROCGEN-UNIQUENESS
       ≥ 95% unique-seeds across 1000-runs
       fingerprint-test : FNV-1a-128 hash of-room-graph divergent
       ¬ visible-repeats within session-window

  M-3  SOVEREIGNTY-ATTESTATION
       0 cap-bleed events ‼ (sovereign-bypass-RECORDED ¬ silent)
       100% audit-trail completeness (per cssl-host-audit canonical-row)
       ConsentZone-bypass = compile-error OR runtime-fault

  M-4  PERFORMANCE
       60fps @ 1440p ; p95 frame-time ≤ 16.7ms
       NPC-population ≥ 4096 city-wide @ 60fps sustained
       Quest-3 budget : ≤ 11.1ms (stereoscopy-ready)

  M-5  MULTIPLAYER-LATENCY
       sync-coop p95-latency ≤ 80ms LAN
       sync-coop p95-latency ≤ 200ms regional
       desync-detection + replay-bit-equal across hosts

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ SCOPE-CUTS  «explicit out-of-scope-now ; ¬ silent-defer»

  ✗ pay-mechanics (real-currency-purchase of in-game-power)
  ✗ gambling-mechanic (loot-box · gacha · randomized-pay)
  ✗ pay-to-win (any axis power-vs-pay correlated)
  ✗ skin-store-as-revenue (cosmetic-pay treated-as-feature-debt)
  ✗ surveillance-telemetry (egress consent-gated ; ¬ default-on)
  ✗ biometric-input (eye-tracking · pulse · facial-affect)
  ✗ user-generated-content moderation backend  (defer post-vertical-slice)
  ✗ competitive-PvP-leaderboards  (defer to later milestone)
  ✗ blockchain · NFT · crypto-currency (¬ now ; ¬ ever per scope)
  ✗ ad-supported tier (¬ surveillance-extraction model)

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ ARCHITECTURE-PRINCIPLES  «structural-discipline ‼ load-bearing»

  R-1  game-logic in `.csl` source ; NEVER plain-Rust
       Rust = compiler-rs HOST-side support OR compiler-output only
       (per feedback_loa_v13_must_be_cssl_source memo)

  R-2  runtime-procgen-mandate
       ¬ hand-authored-content-scenes shipped
       scenes/*.cssl = scaffolding ; throwaway-after-pipeline-verified
       (per feedback_engine_is_runtime_procedural_gen memo)

  R-3  DM/GM/Collab/Coder narrow-orchestrators ; ¬ AGI
       DM = scene-arbiter ; GM = narrator
       Collab = co-author ; Coder = runtime-mutate
       (per 00_THESIS § COROLLARY-1 + feedback_dm_gm_not_general_ai)

  R-4  every-system has stage-0 fallback ; stage-1 KAN-ride opt-in
       deterministic-path ALWAYS-AVAILABLE (08_ROADMAP W6 discipline)
       A/B-tagged audit-rows ; player-sovereign-revoke

  R-5  iterate-everywhere axes  ‼ every-feature ≥ 4-axis touch
       axes : LOGGING · TELEMETRY · TESTING · ROOMS · RENDER · UI
              · INTELLIGENCE · PROCGEN · MULTIPLAYER
       (per 08_ROADMAP § ITERATE-EVERYWHERE-AXES-LEDGER)

  R-6  Σ-mask-per-cell  ‼ structural-consent-encoding
       every-touch sigma_enforce-pass-or-reject
       (per 00_THESIS § COROLLARY-3)

  R-7  cap-gated-outbound + audit-chain
       license-disciplined asset-ingest (CC-BY canonical)
       sovereign-bypass = RECORDED ¬ silent

