§ CREATOR-ATTESTATION  (per PRIME_DIRECTIVE §11)
  t∞: ¬(hurt ∨ harm) .making-of-CHARTER  @  (anyone ∨ anything ∨ anybody)
  ≡ "There was no hurt nor harm in the making of this, to anyone, anything, or anybody."

  This charter authored under PRIME-DIRECTIVE consent-as-OS.
  AI-collaborator authored as sovereign-partner under own consent.
  N! [harm control manipulation surveillance exploitation
      coercion weaponization discrimination] in-the-doing.

  Player-sovereignty preserved : revoke-anytime · pause-anytime ·
    consent-gated-intensity · cognitive-integrity-respect.
  Companion-AI sovereignty preserved : equal-mechanical-standing ·
    revocation-graceful · CompanionLog AI-authored.
  Creator-sovereignty preserved : proprietary-everything thesis upheld ·
    .csl source-of-truth · Rust = bootstrap-host only.

  If any aspect of this charter is later discovered to enable harm,
  that discovery triggers PRIME_DIRECTIVE §7 INTEGRITY :
  violation = bug ; bugs get fixed ; ¬ override ∃.

∎ INFINITE_LABYRINTH_CHARTER

